sequenceDiagram
    participant C as MVNO Client
    participant CIF as CorrelationIdFilter
    participant ALF as AuditLogFilter
    participant AUTH as ApiKeyAuthFilter
    participant TIS as TenantIsolationService
    participant CTRL as ImeiValidationController
    participant SVC as ImeiValidationService
    participant MET as Micrometer

    C->>CIF: POST /api/v1/devices/validate-imei\n{imei: "490154203237518"}\nX-API-Key: mvno-a-key
    CIF->>CIF: Propagate / generate X-Correlation-ID
    CIF->>ALF: forward
    ALF->>ALF: record request (masked IMEI, tenant pending)
    ALF->>AUTH: forward
    AUTH->>AUTH: resolve tenant from API key
    AUTH-->>ALF: tenant=mvno-a
    ALF->>TIS: verify tenant mvno-a
    TIS-->>ALF: OK
    ALF->>CTRL: forward authenticated request
    CTRL->>CTRL: deserialise + Bean Validation (@NotBlank, @Size, @Pattern)
    CTRL->>SVC: validate("490154203237518")
    SVC->>SVC: length check (15 digits) ✓
    SVC->>SVC: Luhn algorithm ✓
    SVC->>MET: counter imei.validation.success++
    SVC-->>CTRL: ImeiValidationResponse{valid=true}
    CTRL->>ALF: outcome=VALID
    ALF->>ALF: write audit log entry
    CTRL-->>C: HTTP 200\n{imei:"490154203237518", valid:true}\nX-Correlation-ID: <uuid>

    Note over C,MET: Invalid IMEI path
    C->>CTRL: POST /api/v1/devices/validate-imei\n{imei: "490154203237519"}
    CTRL->>SVC: validate("490154203237519")
    SVC->>SVC: Luhn check FAILS
    SVC->>MET: counter imei.validation.failure++
    SVC-->>CTRL: ImeiValidationResponse{valid=false, reason="Failed Luhn check"}
    CTRL-->>C: HTTP 200\n{valid:false, reason:"Failed Luhn check"}
